reviewText: My grandson just stood still watching the DVD and smiling. Success!
My grandson loves this video. If he even hears the theme music he gets a big grin on his face and starts dancing in place. he can sit and watch this for hours. Can't wait for volume 2.
Big block is fun for all ages. We have watched this dvd so many times and it never gets old.
Great songs, but buy it at Toys R Us for $10 instead of $35 here.
